Package com.hhstechgroup.tests.regressionBaseline.vii_FacilityEnrollment

This Package contains test classes covering all the test stories for Facility Enrollments.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FacilityEnrollmentRequestForAdditionalInfoAndDenyApplication
    This test class verifies the denial of a Facility enrollment following a Request For Additional Information.
    FacilityEnrollmentSubmitDocumentReview
    This test class verifies the Facility enrollment 'Document Review' status.
    FacilityEnrollmentSubmitScreeningTest
    This test class verifies changing the status of a Facility enrollment from 'Under Screening' to 'Pending Review'.
    FacilityEnrollmentVerifyFingerPrintProcessAndApproveTest
    This test class verifies the Facility enrollment fingerprint work flow.
    FacilityProviderAppealApprovalProcessTest
    This test class verifies approving the appeal of a denied Facility enrollment.
    FacilityProviderAppealDenialProcessTest
    This test class verifies denying the appeal of a denied Facility enrollment.
    FacilityProviderCoCAndAppealApprovalProcessTest
    This test class verifies approving the appeal of a denied Facility CoC.
    FacilityProviderCocDenyProcessTest
    This test class verifies the submission and denial of a Facility Identifying Information CoC.
    FacilityProviderCocProcessTest
    This test class verifies the submission and approval of a Facility Address Details CoC, and verifies the error messages displayed when the creation of a Facility Ownership CoC or a Facility Program Participation CoC is attempted.
    FacilityProviderCreateAndApproveSiteVisitTest
    This test class verifies a Facility Site Visit approval.
    FacilityProviderDenialTest
    This test class verifies the submission of a Facility enrollment.
    FacilityProviderPaymentFeeVerificationTest
    This test class verifies the submission of a Facility enrollment with In-State payment fee verification and a Facility enrollment with Out Of State payment fee verification.
    FacilityProviderPreConditionSetup
    This test class sets the Systems Option configuration for Facility Provider.
    FacilityProviderReenrollmentProcessTest
    This test class verifies the re-enrollment of a Facility Provider.
    FacilityProviderRegistrationAndSubmissionTest
    This test class verifies the submission of a Facility enrollment.
    FacilityProviderRetroActiveAdjustmentApprovalTest
    This test class verifies the Facility Provider enrollment span.
    FacilityProviderRetroActiveRegistrationAndSubmissionTest
    This test class verifies the submission of a retroactive adjustment Facility enrollment.
    FacilityProviderRevalidationVerificationProcessTest
    This test class verifies the Revalidation of a Facility Provider.
    FacilityProviderTerminateSuspendReactiveProcessTest
    This test class verifies the suspension/reactivation of a Facility Provider and the termination and reactivation of a Facility Provider.
